creator: Mary Roberts Rinehart
description:
LibriVox recording of Tish: The Chronicle of Her Escapades and Excursions by Mary Roberts Rinehart.
Read in English by Sandra

The story of three "middle aged ladies". Follow along as they have all sorts of adventures. - Summary by Sandra

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
